                    "Remarks": {
                        "val": "FY14 estimated unit cost differs from FY13 LRIP contracted unit cost due to upgrades from the 2008 Commercial Integrator baseline, which include a Communications Relay Package, EMI Hardening, Turret Upgrade, C2 encryption, an additional datalink, and reliability upgrades.\n\nFY13-FY19 unit cost reflects the contractor delivered system which consists of 5 air vehicles equipped with EO\/IR turret, two ground control stations, one launcher, and one recovery system.\nAncillary equipment consists of payloads (e.g communication relay), ship antennas, and associated equipment (e.g. HMMWVs, tents, Tactical ISR PED System\/Cross Domain System, and mission training devices.)\n\nFY15 shifts primary funding of Government and Contract Engineering Support from RDT&E to PMC."
                    },
